videos.headline: Eastern Michigan's Glass III tosses 4th TD of game
videos.description: Eastern Michigan extends the lead as QB Mike Glass III throws over the middle to connect with Quian Williams for a 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Eastern Michigan's Glass III tosses 4th TD of game) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: Central Connecticut airs it out for go-ahead TD
videos.description: Central Connecticut QB Aaron Winchester goes deep and hits Tyshaun James in stride for a 68-yard touchdown.
